2012-xxxxx: Release 1.1
    * Continued work on making HPMC to be clean C++ internally (and not C).
    * Added ability for HPMC to use specific feature sets of an given OpenGL
      version. Should work using the prescribed core version.
    * Added KHR_debug output (and removed a lot of CHECK_GL).
    * GPGPU pass uses GL_TRIANGLE_STRIP instead of GL_QUADS.
    * Better support for binary fields (e.g. using tables for normals).
    * Removed obsolete transform feedback extensions (supports only 3.0 core)

2009-12-01: Release 1.0.1

    * Fixes some mac-specific issues.


2009-11-29: Release 1.0

    * First public release.
